cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a new approach for estimating indoor room layout from a single-view RGB image using deep learning models. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed approach can have an impact on robotics applications such as robot navigation and mapping. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the proposed approach can be used for scene modeling and augmented reality applications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning models for layout estimation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a new approach for encoding layout information into row vectors and uses dynamic programming for postprocessing.
